msgid "bari.report.non-canonical-scale"
msgstr "Bone Array Rotation Influence: non-canonical armature scale"

msgid "bari.report.non-canonical-scale:description"
msgstr ""
"Inserted fake parent bones have been placed at unexpected position. "
"This may be caused by non-canonical armature scale (like 100). "
"Tweak Offset Distance to more small value if not working properly."

